■ソースコピー元
<Kenji-H/Chatter>
https://github.com/Kenji-H/Chatter.git

以下、参照元Readmeファイル
-----------------------------------------------------------------
1 What's this?
A chat app by Java socket programming.

2 How to start app?
[server] java -jar chatter.jar :port
[client] java -jar chatter.jar :host :port

3 How to stop app?
put "bye" to the command line. (quotes are just for clearity)
-----------------------------------------------------------------